Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.21,0:11:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI Light\c&H323232&\bord0\fs80\pos(1488,1458.665)\frz0.9644}該VR設備的回收 仍然遙遙無期
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\p1\bord3\fscx265\fscy135\3c&H9E78DA&\c&HEBF3F5&\alpha40\pos(1493.332,1504)\frz0.9644}m 0 0 l 0 120 l 370 120 l 370 0 l 0 0
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.12,Main,,0,0,0,,但有消息稱 還有一些是通過黑市途徑交易的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.09,Main,,0,0,0,,就是這個了
